{"id":4271,"date":"2025-06-19T11:43:52","date_gmt":"2025-06-19T04:43:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4271"},"modified":"2025-06-19T11:43:52","modified_gmt":"2025-06-19T04:43:52","slug":"do-ph-cua-da-va-cach-can-bang-do-ph-tren-da","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/do-ph-cua-da-va-cach-can-bang-do-ph-tren-da\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110\u1ed9 pH c\u1ee7a da v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH tr\u00ean da"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0n da kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 l\u00e0 l\u1edbp &#8220;h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o&#8221; b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a da, \u0111\u1ed9 pH \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9 pH tr\u00ean da kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb thay \u0111\u1ed5i do nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da, ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i, hay c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y. C\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u<\/span><\/i><b><i> c\u00e1ch c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH tr\u00ean da <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"do-ph-ly-tuong-cua-da-la-bao-nhieu\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed9 pH l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a da l\u00e0 bao nhi\u00eau?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed9 pH \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o tr\u00ean thang t\u1eeb 0 (axit m\u1ea1nh) \u0111\u1ebfn 14 (ki\u1ec1m m\u1ea1nh). Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u1ed9 pH c\u1ee7a da n\u1eb1m trong kho\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb 4,0 \u0111\u1ebfn 6,5, chi ti\u1ebft nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4327\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4327\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4327\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-1.webp\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9 pH l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a da l\u00e0 bao nhi\u00eau\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4327\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ed9 pH l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a da l\u00e0 bao nhi\u00eau<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1eb7t: Th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH kho\u1ea3ng 4,5 \u2013 6,2, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng theo tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c. M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng, y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 di truy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da c\u01a1 th\u1ec3: C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n, t\u1eeb kho\u1ea3ng 5,5 \u2013 6,5.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"vi-sao-can-bang-do-ph-cua-da-lai-rat-quan-trong\"><\/span><b>V\u00ec sao c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH c\u1ee7a da l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4328\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4328\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4328\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-2.webp\" alt=\"V\u00ec sao c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH c\u1ee7a da l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4328\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">V\u00ec sao c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH c\u1ee7a da l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c duy tr\u00ec c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH cho da tuy \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-ve-lop-mang-tu-nhien-cua-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da lu\u00f4n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng lipid t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c axit b\u00e9o v\u00e0 ceramides, c\u00f3 t\u00ednh axit nh\u1eb9. L\u1edbp m\u00e0ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap da ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i vi khu\u1ea9n, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi \u0111\u1ed9 pH da b\u1ecb r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n, h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y suy y\u1ebfu, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nguy c\u01a1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, bong tr\u00f3c, nhi\u1ec5m khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c. Do \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH s\u1ebd gi\u1eef l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng lipid v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"giu-gin-do-am-ly-tuong-cua-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1eef g\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed9 pH c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u00fap l\u1edbp s\u1eebng (l\u1edbp ngo\u00e0i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a da) duy tr\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc. Cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. Khi m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH, l\u1edbp s\u1eebng s\u1ebd y\u1ebfu \u0111i, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, khi\u1ebfn da kh\u00f4, c\u0103ng r\u00e1t, v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 bong tr\u00f3c. Duy tr\u00ec pH \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n \u1ea9m m\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-dem-tang-hieu-qua-cham-soc-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 pH t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean tr\u00ean da. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9 pH c\u1ee7a da b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ed9 pH \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. Mang l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da cao nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhung-van-de-xay-ra-khi-do-ph-tren-da-mat-can-bang\"><\/span><b>Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 x\u1ea3y ra khi \u0111\u1ed9 pH tr\u00ean da m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi \u0111\u1ed9 pH b\u1ecb thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng, l\u00e0n da s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed9 pH qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p (qu\u00e1 axit): Da ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn h\u01a1n, l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng gi\u00e3n to, t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 v\u00e0 vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed9 pH qu\u00e1 cao (qu\u00e1 ki\u1ec1m): L\u00e0n da s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm nh\u01b0 n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n, kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u00edch \u1ee9ng, vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m: Khi pH m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, da d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf, s\u01b0ng t\u1ea5y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3: L\u1edbp b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da suy y\u1ebfu. Khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nguyen-nhan-gay-mat-can-bang-ph-tren-da\"><\/span><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH tr\u00ean da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed9 pH:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4329\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4329\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4329\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-3.webp\" alt=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH tr\u00ean da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4329\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH tr\u00ean da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p: C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH qu\u00e1 cao ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p so v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. L\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da sai c\u00e1ch: R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 n\u00f3ng. Ho\u1eb7c ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t m\u1ea1nh khi v\u1ec7 sinh da c\u0169ng g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng thi\u1ebfu c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng: \u0102n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a t\u00ednh ki\u1ec1m. Ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m mang t\u00ednh axit s\u1ebd g\u00e2y bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 pH c\u1ee7a l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"top-5-cach-hieu-qua-de-can-bang-do-ph-cho-lan-da\"><\/span><b>Top 5 c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH cho l\u00e0n da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4330\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4330\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4330\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-4.webp\" alt=\"Top 5 c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH cho l\u00e0n da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/54-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4330\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Top 5 c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH cho l\u00e0n da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chon-san-pham-cham-soc-da-co-do-ph-phu-hop\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH th\u00edch h\u1ee3p l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u1ed9 pH l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a l\u00e0n da th\u01b0\u1eddng dao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 4,5 \u0111\u1ebfn 5,5, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng axit nh\u1eb9. Khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 pH chu\u1ea9n. L\u00e0n da s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Duy tr\u00ec h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean: Da c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng axit b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. Gi\u00fap ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 vi khu\u1ea9n, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n. D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00fang pH gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng n\u00e0y, gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba da m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc: C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH cao (t\u00ednh ki\u1ec1m) th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1edbp s\u1eebng tr\u00ean da. D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p s\u1ebd gi\u1eef \u1ea9m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfi kh\u00f4 n\u1ebb.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 vi\u00eam da: \u0110\u1ed9 pH axit nh\u1eb9 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean tr\u00ean da ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 n\u1ea5m ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. Khi \u0111\u1ed9 pH \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, l\u00e0n da \u00edt b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf. Hay vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khong-su-dung-nuoc-qua-nong-khi-lam-sach-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 n\u00f3ng khi l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 n\u00f3ng khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ho\u1eb7c t\u1eafm c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH c\u1ee7a l\u00e0n da, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m m\u1ea5t l\u1edbp d\u1ea7u b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean: N\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y \u0111i l\u1edbp d\u1ea7u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean (m\u00e0ng lipid) tr\u00ean da. G\u00e2y suy y\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH: N\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00f3ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m thay \u0111\u1ed5i nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean tr\u00ean da. D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u00edch th\u00edch c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 da li\u1ec5u: Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, eczema ho\u1eb7c vi\u00eam da s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00f3ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luon-dung-toner-ngay-sau-khi-rua-mat\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lu\u00f4n d\u00f9ng toner ngay sau khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng toner sau khi l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng da: Toner th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n nh\u1eb9 d\u1ecbu nh\u01b0 hoa sen, l\u00f4 h\u1ed9i ho\u1eb7c tr\u00e0 xanh. C\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho l\u00e0n da ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c: Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 glycerin hay hyaluronic acid trong toner gi\u00fap gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc. Mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, c\u0103ng m\u01b0\u1edbt su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y.<\/span>&nbsp;<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u00e0n da cho c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc skincare ti\u1ebfp theo: Toner gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH nhanh ch\u00f3ng. Gi\u00fap da d\u1ec5 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1i \u01b0u.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft GSC chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y n\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9 pH tr\u00ean da l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 \u201c<\/span><b>c\u00e1ch c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u201d tr\u00ean da r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00fang kh\u00f4ng n\u00e0o? \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean gh\u00e9 th\u0103m wesbite c\u1ee7a GSC m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ed5 c\u1eadp nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da n\u1eefa nh\u00e1!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110\u1ed9 pH tr\u00ean da kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb thay \u0111\u1ed5i do nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da, ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i, hay c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y. C\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH tr\u00ean da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4331,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4271","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4271","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4271"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4271\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4333,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4271\/revisions\/4333"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4331"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4271"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4271"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4271"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}